<div class="bg-gray-50 min-h-screen py-12">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">요금제</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        누수체크는 성공 수수료 기반으로 운영됩니다.<br>
        초기 비용 없이 시작하고, 작업 완료 시에만 수수료가 발생합니다.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- 고객 요금 -->
    <div class="mb-20">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">고객 요금</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">누수 문제를 해결하고 싶으신가요?</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <!-- AI 빠른 점검 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden transform hover:scale-105 transition duration-300">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-600 to-purple-800 text-white p-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">AI 빠른 점검</h3>
            <div class="flex items-baseline">
              <span class="text-5xl font-bold">무료</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8">
            <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">회원가입 불필요</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">AI 기반 즉시 분석</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">심각도 5단계 평가</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">추천 조치 사항 제공</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <%= link_to "지금 시작하기 →", ai_quick_inspection_new_path, class: "block w-full text-center bg-purple-600 text-white font-semibold py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-purple-700 transition" %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 전문가 매칭 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden transform hover:scale-105 transition duration-300 ring-4 ring-blue-500 relative">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-blue-500 text-white px-4 py-1 text-sm font-semibold rounded-bl-lg">
            인기
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-800 text-white p-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">전문가 매칭</h3>
            <div class="flex items-baseline">
              <span class="text-5xl font-bold">무료</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-blue-100 text-sm mt-2">플랫폼 이용료 없음</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8">
            <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">검증된 전문가 연결</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">안전한 에스크로 결제</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">실시간 진행 상황 확인</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">하자보수 보증</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">보험청구 서류 자동화</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <%= link_to "체크 접수하기 →", new_customers_request_path, class: "block w-full text-center bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition" %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 실제 비용 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-700 to-gray-900 text-white p-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">실제 지불 비용</h3>
            <div class="text-gray-300 text-sm">전문가에게 직접 지불</div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8">
            <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
              <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-4">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
                  <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">출장비</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-600">₩50,000~</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">현장 방문 비용</p>
              </div>

              <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-4">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
                  <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">탐지비</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-600">₩100,000~</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">누수 위치 탐지</p>
              </div>

              <div class="pb-4">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
                  <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">공사비</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-600">₩200,000~</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">실제 수리 작업 (VAT 포함)</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4">
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                <strong class="text-gray-900">투명한 표준 견적</strong><br>
                모든 비용은 전문가의 표준 견적서로 확인할 수 있으며,
                승인 후에만 에스크로 결제가 진행됩니다.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 전문가 요금 -->
    <div class="mb-20">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">전문가 (마스터) 요금</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">누수 전문가로 활동하고 싶으신가요?</p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-600 to-green-800 text-white p-8">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center">
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">성공 수수료제</h3>
                <p class="text-green-100">작업 완료 시에만 수수료 발생</p>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-4 md:mt-0">
                <div class="flex items-baseline">
                  <span class="text-6xl font-bold">15%</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-green-100 text-center mt-2">공사비 기준</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="p-8">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-900 mb-4">포함 사항</h4>
                <ul class="space-y-3">
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-gray-700">안정적인 고객 매칭</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-gray-700">에스크로 대금 보장</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-gray-700">자동 정산 시스템</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-gray-700">표준 견적 시스템</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-900 mb-4">추가 혜택</h4>
                <ul class="space-y-3">
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-gray-700">대시보드 및 통계</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-gray-700">고객 리뷰 시스템</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-gray-700">실시간 알림</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-gray-700">공개 프로필 페이지</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-blue-900 mb-3">수수료 계산 예시</h4>
              <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                <div class="flex justify-between">
                  <span class="text-gray-700">공사비 (VAT 포함)</span>
                  <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">₩1,000,000</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between text-red-600">
                  <span>플랫폼 수수료 (15%)</span>
                  <span class="font-semibold">-₩150,000</span>
                </div>
                <div class="border-t border-blue-200 pt-2 flex justify-between text-lg">
                  <span class="font-bold text-blue-900">전문가 수령 금액</span>
                  <span class="font-bold text-green-600">₩850,000</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <%= link_to "전문가로 등록하기 →", new_expert_registration_path, class: "block w-full text-center bg-green-600 text-white font-semibold py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-green-700 transition text-lg" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-12">자주 묻는 질문</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-900 cursor-pointer">고객은 어떤 비용을 지불하나요?</summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">고객은 플랫폼 이용료 없이 전문가에게 작업비용만 직접 지불합니다. 출장비, 탐지비, 공사비는 전문가의 표준 견적에 따라 결정되며, 승인 후 에스크로 결제로 안전하게 거래됩니다.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-900 cursor-pointer">에스크로 결제는 어떻게 작동하나요?</summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">고객이 결제한 금액은 플랫폼이 안전하게 보관합니다. 작업 완료 후 고객이 확인하면 관리자 검토를 거쳐 전문가에게 정산됩니다. 분쟁 발생 시 환불도 가능합니다.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-900 cursor-pointer">전문가 수수료는 언제 발생하나요?</summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">수수료는 공사 완료 및 고객 확인 후 정산 시점에만 발생합니다. 작업을 진행하지 않거나 중단된 경우 수수료가 발생하지 않습니다.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-900 cursor-pointer">AI 빠른 점검은 정말 무료인가요?</summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">네, AI 빠른 점검은 100% 무료입니다. 회원가입 없이도 사진만 업로드하면 즉시 AI 분석 결과를 받을 수 있습니다. 누수 심각도와 추천 조치 사항을 확인하세요.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-900 cursor-pointer">출장비나 탐지비는 수수료에 포함되나요?</summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">아니요. 플랫폼 수수료 15%는 공사비 기준으로만 계산됩니다. 출장비와 탐지비는 전문가가 100% 수령합니다.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="mt-20 text-center bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-800 text-white rounded-2xl p-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">지금 바로 시작하세요</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 mb-8">투명하고 안전한 누수 해결 플랫폼, 누수체크</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <%= link_to "고객으로 시작하기", new_user_registration_path, class: "px-8 py-4 bg-white text-blue-600 font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-50 transition transform hover:scale-105" %>
        <%= link_to "전문가로 시작하기", new_expert_registration_path, class: "px-8 py-4 bg-blue-500 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-400 transition transform hover:scale-105" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
